      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAYNE CARGO (1) is a promising type who notched his 6th career success when too good (17.57) at this track last time. Strike rate this distance strong having won four of five tries. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Has put together a string of wins and expected to go close again. LINKIN PARK (4) is in hot form winning her last three on end, the latest pinging the lids with a fast early split and clocking 17.21 over 300m at this track. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Hard to fault her form and makes plenty of appeal again. AT THE GATE (2) has been in sparkling form recording back to back wins, the latest at this track last time over 300m in (17.37). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Leading player again. MIDNIGHT DASH (8) pinged the lids and wasn't headed last time. Sure to figure prominently.",
